I am very curious because I&#039;m Azir main myself and I really want his kit to remain unchanged. Personaly I want his ultimate to be 3/4/5 seconds instead of 3 seconds at all ranks, that&#039;s what I really want. Because his ultimate is not only for Shurima Shuffle its for peeling late game for yourself and carries and 3 seconds is simply not enough. It would be great if you can tell us all what should we expect from it and what it should be like.

-Thanks

-Fellow Azir Main {{champion:268}}
